import React from 'react'
import FormHeader from '../components/FormHeader'
import CenteredTabs from '../components/Tabs'
import QuestionForm from '../components/QuestionForm'

function FormPage() {
  return (
    <>
    <FormHeader/>
    <CenteredTabs />
    <QuestionForm />
    </>
  )
}

export default FormPage
